# Spicy Chicken and Tinned Tomatoes

A simple, cheap and healthy dish.

- ‚è≤Ô∏è Prep time: 5
- üç≥Cook time: 10
- üçΩÔ∏è Servings: 1-2

## Ingredients

- Tin of chopped tomatoes (one per person)
- Chicken Brest (1 large or 2 small per person)
- Seasoning for chicken e.g Cajun Spice Mix
- Salt and Black Pepper
- Chili flakes
- Butter


## Directions

1. Butterfly the chicken breasts, season to taste
2. Place the tinned tomatoes in a pan and reduce
3. Season tomatoes with the salt and pepper, add chili flakes to taste 
4. Melt small nob of butter in a heavy skillet or pan and cook the chicken.
5. Once cooked plate up chicken and pour over your tomatoes


